Usage of map_editor :

Button GENERATION : Generate a map using the parameter N.

Button SAVE : Save the current map in the current directory using
the 'File' name.

Button LOAD : Load a map from a file in the current directory
whose name is in the 'File' field.

Button LOAD TYPES : Load the attributs of the pulsars from the
file TYPES in the current directory.

Button UPDATE : Use the value you modified in the fields for
the attributs of the pulsars.

Edition of the map : Left click to modify any case. It will get
the attributs from the check-list at the right.

Format of a map :

N \\ Size of the map
nb \\ Number of pulsars in the map
period_1 time_1 power_1 \\ Attributs of pulsar #1
...
period_nb time_nb power_nb \\ Attributs of pulsar #nb
map_line_1 \\ '#' for a pulsar, 'B' for a base and '.' else
...
map_line_N
type_pulsar_1 \\ This part is optional (it's only necessary to
              \\ load back the map in the editor)
...
type_pulsar_5
